d
06A116~&28A11L/  Pentru ce curent care parcurge o rezistenta de 100&Omega; se realizeaza o putere disipata de 100 W?
null
 0,125A 		
 0,25A
 0,5A 			
 1A
Subiect public ANRCTI, 2007
null
P = U*I = (R*I)*I = R * I<sup>2</sup>; Rezulta I = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">P/R</span>= &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">100W/100&Omega;</span> = 1 A;
YO6OWN, Brasov, 2007
##28#
a
07A116~&29C11L/  Pentru ce curent care parcurge o rezistenta de 10k&Omega; se realizeaza o putere disipata de 100 W?
null
 0,1A 		
 0,125A
 0,15A 		
 0,2A
Subiect public ANRCTI, 2007
null
P = U*I = (R*I)*I = R * I<sup>2</sup>; Rezulta I = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">P/R</span>= &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">100W/10k&Omega;</span> = 0.1 A;
