##372#
a
01B324~&07D32K/ La un circuit rezonant paralel capacitatea totala de acord variaza intre valoarea minima Cm = 20pF si cea maxima CM = 180 pF. Daca inductanta circuitului ramane constanta, cat este valoarea raportului intre frecventa maxima de acord fM (corespunzatoare lui Cm) si cea minima fm (corespunzatoare lui CM)?
null
 fM/fm = 3	
 fM/fm = 2,5
 fM/fm = 2	
 fM/fm = 1,5
Subiect public ANRCTI, 2007
null
Folosim formula Thomson: f = 1/(2* &pi; * &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L * C</span>); De aici fM / fm =   &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L * CM</span> / &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L * Cm</span> = (&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L</span> * &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">CM</span>) / (&radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">L</span> * &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">Cm</span>) =  &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">CM</span> / &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">CM</span> = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">CM/Cm</span> = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">180/20</span> = &radic;<span style="text-decoration:overline">9</span> = 3     
YO6OWN, Brasov, 2007
##373#
c
