Ri = (Ugol-Usarcina) / I = (16V-12V)/2A = 2&Omega;<br>Transferul maxim de putere intre doua etaje are loc atunci cand intre cele doua etaje exista adaptare perfecta: Z<sub>out</sub>=Z<sub>in</sub>, adica Ri=Rs.<br>Rs=2&Omega;
YO6OWN, Brasov, 2008
